          <h3 class="blog-editorial__title">5 Ways to Transform Your Bedroom into a Luxury Sleep Sanctuary</h3>
          <p class="blog-editorial__excerpt">Your bedroom is the most important room in your home — yet most people spend less time designing it than their living room. A few considered changes can completely transform how you feel at the end of each day. Start with your bed frame: an upholstered wing-back or statement panel bed instantly elevates the room. Layer your bedding with natural fibres — cotton, linen, or bamboo — for temperature regulation. Keep colours calm: soft creams, warm greys, and earthy tones signal sleep to your brain. Invest in blackout curtains and consider a bedside reading lamp on a warm dimmer. Finally, declutter ruthlessly — a calm, uncluttered bedroom promotes deeper, faster sleep. Our luxury bed frames are designed specifically to anchor a restful bedroom aesthetic.</p>
